heart transplant surgeries till 2012.<ref>{{cite web |title=Missing links |url=https://www.theweek.in/health/cover/2018/06/16/missing-links.html |website=The Week |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=\u09aa\u09cd\u09b0\u09be\u09af\u09bc \u09e8\u09e6\u09e6 \u09b0\u09cb\u0997\u09c0\u09b0 \u09b9\u09c3\u09a6\u09af\u09bc \u09aa\u09cd\u09b0\u09a4\u09bf\u09b8\u09cd\u09a5\u09be\u09aa\u09a8 \u0995\u09b0\u09b2\u09c7\u09a8 \u09a4\u09bf\u09a8\u09bf |url=https://eisamay.indiatimes.com/nation/dr-k-r-balakrishnan-at-fortis-is-well-experienced-cardiothoracic-surgery-doctor/articleshow/64267022.cms |work=Eisamay |date=22 May 2018 |language=bn}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Chennai: High risk lung transplant done |url=https://www.deccanchronicle.com/nation/current-affairs/220818/chennai-high-risk-lung-transplant-done.html |website=Deccan Chronicle |language=en |date=22 August 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Nag |first1=Jayatri NagJayatri |last2=May 21 |first2=Bangalore Mirror Bureau |title=Bengaluru man\u2019s heart flown to Kolkata, cops create green corridor for transplant|url=https://bangaloremirror.indiatimes.com/bangalore/others/bengaluru-mans-heart-flown-to-kolkata-cops-create-green-corridor-for-transplant/articleshow/64261209.cms |work=Bangalore Mirror |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Strong-Willed Man Who Underwent Heart Transplant Three Years Ago Is Now Running Marathons |url=https://www.indiatimes.com/news/india/strong-willed-man-who-underwent-heart-transplant-three-years-ago-is-now-running-marathons-360206.html |website=indiatimes.com |language=en |date=11 January 2019}}</ref>\n\nHe has successfully performed by pass surgery of a shop owner from Gujarat \"Jaisukhabi Thakur\" who had no pulse rate.<ref>{{cite news |title=45 minutes after heart stops, man revived, gets new heart |url=https://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/chennai/45-minutes-after-heart-stops-man-revived-gets-new-heart/article8496269.ece |work=The Hindu |date=20 April 2016 |language=en-IN}}<